="#000000" operatercreater="0">        签名日期</span><input name="日期" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">      年   月   日</span></input><p operatercreater="0" /><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">如果患者无法签署知情同意书，请其授权的亲属在此签名：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">患者授权亲属签名</span><span forecolor="#000000" fontunderline="1" operatercreater="0">          </span><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0"> 与患者关系</span><span forecolor="#000000" fontunderline="1" operatercreater="0">          </span><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">  签名日期</span><input name="日期" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">      年   月   日</span></input><p operatercreater="0" /></cell></row><row id="C57F6121347" width="660" operatercreater="0"><cell id="C57F6121348" width="660" operatercreater="0"><span fontbold="1" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">医生陈述</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    我已经告知患者将要进行的手术方式、此次手术及术后可能发生的并发症和风险、可能存在的其它治疗方法并且解答了患者关于此次手术的相关问题。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><p operatercreater="0" /><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">医师签名</span><input name="医师签名" operatercreater="0"><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">     </span></input><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">                          签名日期</span><input name="日期" operatercreater="0"><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">      年   月   日</span></input><p operatercreater="0" /></cell></row></table><p operatercreater="0" /></body></emrtextdoc></body></emrtextdoc>